1. Receive file (CSV / XLSX)
2. Read file
3. Infer schema
4. Check if table exists
   ├─ If NOT → CREATE TABLE
   ├─ If YES → Compare schema
       ├─ Missing columns → ALTER TABLE
       ├─ Same schema → continue
5. Insert data
6. Log metadata



